Class JacksonifiedConnectionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rabbitmq.client.ConnectionFactory
      • io.druid.firehose.rabbitmq.JacksonifiedConnectionFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class JacksonifiedConnectionFactory
extends com.rabbitmq.client.ConnectionFactory
    A Jacksonified version of the RabbitMQ ConnectionFactory for better integration into the realtime.spec configuration file format.
